     |--------------------------|-----------------------------------|----------------------------------------|
     | Traditional usage        | Traditional way to handle Promises| Modern way to handle Promises          |
     | Syntax                   | Callback-based                    | Looks like synchronous code            |
     | Readability              | Less clean with chaining          | More readable and cleaner              |
     | Error handling           | Uses `.catch()`                   | Uses `try...catch`                     |
     | Use case                 | Simple chains                     | Complex flows, loops, conditions       | -->
